  "summary": "Agentic AI success depends on judgment, boundaries, and accountability.",
  "body": "Agentic AI is not simply automation.\n\nThe challenge is deciding:\n\n- what should be autonomous\n- what should remain human\n- when escalation is required\n- what evidence is sufficient\n- who remains accountable\n\nJoz approaches agentic systems as decision systems.\n\nThe objective is not maximum autonomy.\n\nThe objective is appropriate autonomy supported by trust, governance, observability, and clear ownership.",
